    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1954-06-16T16:18:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1954-06-16T16:18:00-05:00" n="191"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d191">
                <head>191. Telegram From the <gloss type="from">Central Intelligence Agency</gloss>
                    to <gloss type="to">Operation <gloss target="#t_PBSPBSUCCESS1">PBSUCCESS</gloss>
                        Headquarters in Florida</gloss>
                    <note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d191fn1">Source: Central Intelligence Agency,
                        Job 79–010125A, Box 9, Folder 2. Secret; Priority; RYBAT; <gloss
                            target="#t_PBSPBSUCCESS1">PBSUCCESS</gloss>. Drafted by <persName
                            corresp="#p_WFHSW1">Wisner</persName>.</note>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian"
                        when="1954-06-16T21:18:00+00:00">June 16, 1954, 2118Z</date>.</dateline>
                <p>05145. Ref: A. GUAT 848;<note n="2" xml:id="d191fn2">See <ref target="#d188fn2"
                            >footnote 2, Document 188</ref>.</note> B. <gloss target="#t_LINC1"
                        >LINC</gloss> 3895.<note n="3" xml:id="d191fn3">
                        <ref target="#d188">Document 188</ref>.</note>
                </p>
                <list>
                    <label>1.</label>
                    <item>As indicated <persName corresp="#p_WHS1">Whiting</persName>/<persName
                            corresp="#p_PWD1">Playdon</persName> telephone conversation, we believe
                            <gloss target="#t_LINC1">LINC</gloss> made correct decision in return of
                        Page to <gloss target="#t_WSBURNT1">WSBURNT</gloss>.<note n="4"
                            xml:id="d191fn4">See <ref target="#d186">Document 186</ref>.</note>
                        Whereas we recognize validity and serious import of certain points in
                        reference A message, this appears time for calculated risk taken with eyes
                        open in order obtain maximum results from Page knowledge, ability and
                        relationship with [<hi rend="italic">name not declassified</hi>]. The
                        overriding importance of what could be produced as a result success this
                        line of effort is clear to everyone here, especially in light of developing
                        difficulties and increasing uncertainties <persName corresp="#p_CJH1"
                            >Calligeris</persName> effort.</item>
                    <label>2.</label>
                    <item>Our only suggestion is that you may wish instruct Station to prepare plan
                        for Embassy action in event Page arrest or disappearance. Do not believe
                        Page should remain <gloss target="#t_WSBURNT1">WSBURNT</gloss> more than
                        minimum time enable him establish contact and deliver final
                        exhortation.</item>
                </list>
            </div>
        </body>
